name: Farting Unicorn
description: Farting Unicorn ($FU) is a 100% community-driven cryptocurrency designed to bring fun, innovation, and transparency to the blockchain ecosystem. Evolving from its origins as a lighthearted concept, $FU has become a unique project that combines community collaboration, decentralized governance, and impactful utility. This whitepaper outlines the vision, technical framework, use cases, and roadmap for $FU.
